org.gbif.dwc.record

Class DarwinCoreRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.dwc.record.DarwinCoreTaxon
      • org.gbif.dwc.record.DarwinCoreRecord

  • public class DarwinCoreRecord
extends DarwinCoreTaxon
    A bean representing a simple Darwin Core record with a property for each dwc term apart from terms of group MeasurementOrFact or ResourceRelationship.
